---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CtaSection from '../components/CtaSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Therapist Near Alameda, CA | EMDR & Anxiety | Maren Voss"
  description="Oakland-based therapist serving Alameda residents. EMDR, trauma, anxiety, and burnout therapy. In-person and telehealth."
>
  <Header slot="header" />

  <section class="interior-hero section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="heading-page">Therapist Near Alameda</h1>
      <p class="interior-hero__tagline">Oakland-based therapist, a short drive from the island.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>Alameda is a quick trip from my Rockridge office, and for residents who prefer to stay on the island, telehealth sessions are a full alternative.</p>
        <p>I work with Alameda residents who are looking for therapy that goes deeper than what they've found through general directory searches. If you've been wanting to try EMDR, are interested in a therapist who specializes in trauma or anxiety rather than a generalist approach, or are simply looking for someone who will be direct and real with you, I'd welcome a conversation.</p>
        <p>Whether you're dealing with burnout from a demanding career across the Bay, navigating a life transition, or carrying something from your past that's still affecting your present, the work we do together can help.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-dark section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="body-text">
        <p>I specialize in <a href="/trauma-ptsd" class="text-link-dark">trauma & PTSD</a>, <a href="/anxiety" class="text-link-dark">anxiety</a>, <a href="/burnout" class="text-link-dark">burnout and high-achiever stress</a>, <a href="/relationship-patterns" class="text-link-dark">relationship patterns</a>, and <a href="/life-transitions" class="text-link-dark">life transitions</a>. My approach integrates EMDR, IFS, and somatic therapy.</p>
        <p><a href="/how-i-work" class="text-link-dark">Learn more about how I work &rarr;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-cream section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="geo-info">
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Office</h2>
          <p>5432 College Ave, Suite 204, Oakland, CA 94618</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">From Alameda</h2>
          <p>10-15 minutes via I-880 or surface streets</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Telehealth</h2>
          <p>Available for all California residents.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="geo-info__item">
          <h2 class="heading-sub">Getting Started</h2>
          <p><a href="/contact" class="text-link-light">Schedule a free 15-minute consultation &rarr;</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaSection />
  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .interior-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--section-pad) + 72px);
  }

  .interior-hero__tagline {
    color: var(--text-muted-light);
    font-size: var(--body);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .body-text p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .body-text p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .geo-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px 64px;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .geo-info__item h2 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .geo-info__item p {
    font-size: var(--body-small);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .geo-info {
      gap: 40px 48px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .geo-info {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
